Ford Motor Co said it hasextended to April 30 its buyer incentive program on 1986 and1987 Ford Escort and Tempo, and Mercury Lynx and Topaz.    Consumers will have a choice of 3.9 pct to 9.9 pct annualpercentage rate financing or a cash rebate of up to 600 dlrs.    Earlier Ford extended its incentive program to April 30 onits Taurus and Mercury Sable and several lines of light trucks. Reuter&#3;